							<div class="bio-container">
					<div class="bio-img-container">
						<div class="bio-img">
							<img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Hannah-Bonner-100x100.jpg" width="96" height="96" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Hannah-Bonner-300x300.jpg 2x" alt="Hannah Bonner" class="avatar avatar-96 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-96 alignnone photo" />						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Hannah Bonner</h4>
												<p>Hannah Bonner is the author of <em>Another Woman</em> (EastOver Press 2024). Her writing has appeared in <em>BOMB, Cleveland Review of Books, Literary Hub, the Los Angeles Review of Books,</em> and <em>The Sewanee Review</em>, among others. She lives in Philadelphia.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			
